channel.title: It just quits
channel.description: Hi, I'm on a mac os X 10.4.8, and i have downloaded moparscape. I unzipped it and clicked on 'moparscape.jar' and it opens but after a couple seconds it just quits without even any error message. I haven't changed anything and java is working just fine, all the files that came with the download are still in the folder but i don't have any idea why it is doing this. Help!
